        </p>
        <p>
          Build quality is professional-grade with magnesium alloy construction and comprehensive weather sealing. The LP-E6P battery provides approximately 310 shots per charge (CIPA), though real-world performance often exceeds 500 shots with power-saving settings. Dual CFexpress Type B / SD card slots support various workflow needs. USB-C Power Delivery enables continuous operation for extended shoots.
